(53, 1, '2021-01-13 05:31:01', '2021-01-13 05:31:01', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Renesas Electronics Corporation announces its collaboration with Microsoft to accelerate the development of <strong>connected vehicles</strong>. <strong>Renesas’ R-Car Starter Kit, </strong>based on<strong> Renesas’ R-Car automotive system-on-chip (SoC)</strong>, is now available as a development environment for the <strong>Microsoft Connected Vehicle Platform (MCVP)</strong>. MCVP combines a partner ecosystem with a horizontal platform of Azure cloud, AI and edge services on top of which mobility companies can build customer-facing solutions. Renesas has also been certified for <strong>Azure IoT Hub and Azure IoT Edge</strong>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Accelerate Connected Vehicle Development', 'Renesas Electronics Corporation announces its collaboration with Microsoft to accelerate the development of connected vehicles. Renesas’ R-Car Starter Kit,', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'accelerate-connected-vehicle-development', '', '', '2021-01-13 05:32:17', '2021-01-13 05:32:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/electronics/?p=53', 0, 'post', '', 0),
